[Method]
Load
[Function]
dcl_SlideView_Load
[Desc]
This method loads a slide image or slide library and then displays the slide in the control.
[Arguments]
<CONTROL>
\par\tab FileName
[as String]
\par\tab\i{Optional} \i0 SlideLibraryImageName
[as String]


[Method]
Clear
[Function]
dcl_SlideView_Clear
[Desc]
This method clears the control.
[Arguments]
<CONTROL>


[Method]
SlideImage
[Function]
dcl_SlideView_SlideImage
[Desc]
This method will load a slide image from a slide file or slide library file and paint it anywhere on the control.
[Arguments]
<CONTROL>
\par\tab 
[Begin List]
[Begin List]
\par\tab UpperLeftX
[as Integer]
\par\tab UpperLeftY
[as Integer]
\par\tab Width
[as Integer]
\par\tab Height
[as Integer]
\par\tab FileName
[as String]
\par\tab\i{Optional} \i0 SlideLibraryImageName
[as String]
[End List]
\par\tab ...
[End List]


[Method]
